Zhejiang Tantech Bamboo Technology Co., Ltd. was established in October 2002. It is a leading high-tech enterprise, specializing in the R&D, manufacturing and sales of bamboo charcoal products for use as EDLC carbon materials, air purification products and charcoal briquettes.
The company was founded in the rapidly developing city of Lishui, Zhejiang Province, in Southeast China, which contains one of China's largest areas of bamboo forestland. The company possesses two large factories in Lishui, one located in Tianning Industrial District, with a total land area of 4.13 acres as well as a new 9.67 acre land area factory in Shuige industrial district.
Tantech has undertaken and completed nearly 20 national, provincial and municipal scientific research projects. The Company also has participated in the development of three national scientific standards and has been awarded with the National Science and Technology Award. The Company possesses more than 10 patents. It also possesses the ISO: 9001 certificate, the ISO: 14000 Certificate, as well as the China Ministry of Agriculture Organic Product Certification. All of which have helped the company take a leading position in the charcoal materials industry and sustain key competitive advantages.
Tantech’s R&D department is led by science and engineering professionals with strong academic backgrounds and decades of experience. The Company continues to invest heavily in its R&D in order to elevate itself in the EDLC carbon industry.
The company has established a developed sales and logistics network. Its products are sold in supermarkets, such as Wal-Mart and Carrefour throughout China. Additionally, these products are sold internationally in all parts of the world, including the U.S., Japan, Korea, Singapore, Taiwan, Europe and the Middle East. The company also preserves important ties with global EDLC companies.
Tantech maintains key relationships with local governments, academic institutions, local banks and forestry associations in order to sustain itself as a major industry player. Additionally, the Company has crucial relationships with bamboo suppliers, ensuring low prices and high quality of raw materials.
Tantech’s development goal is to constantly adhere to green and environmentally conscious development and to sharpen its technological base in order to expand its domestic and global market share, allowing Tantech to become the leading global enterprise in the bamboo charcoal industry.






