The company is committed to  continual research and development of bamboo charcoal for various applications,  as R&D is the backbone and heart of it’s operations. The Company adheres to the principles of scientific  and technological innovation to move itself forward under its long-term plan. The  company regularly collaborates with a number of  world-renown universities institutions in the advancement of charcoal bamboo  research. Cooperations and partnerships with these institutions are critical in  the 


development of major scientific research projects. Many of these  universities are supported by China’s  central government, as well as provincial and municipal governments.  Collaborations with these institutions involve projects covering bamboo  vinegar, quality of bamboo optimization, strength of bamboo, technical  training, technology exchange and integration, as well as processes of  carbonizing bamboo. 











 










